Acid Rain.name: Acid Rain
Acid Rain.description: Creates acidic clouds that pour down acid rain on enemies

Air Blade.name: Air Blade
Air Blade.description: Sends out sharp blades of air in a fan shape.

Air Cannon.name: Air Cannon
Air Cannon.description: Quickly fires a burst of highly pressurized air.

Apocalypse.name: Apocalypse
Apocalypse.description: Generates several dark vortexes in the surrounding area.

Aqua Burst.name: Aqua Burst
Aqua Burst.description: Creates a giant ball of water and hurls it at an enemy.

Aqua Gun.name: Aqua Gun
Aqua Gun.description: Hurls a ball of water straight at an enemy.

Beam Slicer.name: Beam Slicer
Beam Slicer.description: Mows down the frontal area with a beam imbued with dragon power. The area touched by the beam will also explode after a few moments.

Blast Cannon.name: Blast Cannon
Blast Cannon.description: Fires an energy bullet imbued with dragon power at the enemy's location. Upon impact, the bullet shatters and creates a frontal long-range explosion.

Blizzard Spike.name: Blizzard Spike
Blizzard Spike.description: Creates a giant lump of ice and hurls it at any enemy. It deals damage to those in the surrounding area upon impact.

Bog Blast.name: Bog Blast
Bog Blast.description: Hurls sticky mud at an enemy.

Bubble Blast.name: Bubble Blast
Bubble Blast.description: Fires numerous bubbles that slowly pursue an enemy.

Circle Vine.name: Circle Vine
Circle Vine.description: Sprots sharp roots in and around the enemy's location.

Comet Strike.name: Comet Strike
Comet Strike.description: Drops a meteorite straight down, generating a shock wave around the impact area.

Cryst Breath.name: Cryst Breath
Cryst Breath.description: Enshrouds an enemy in a frigid blast of air, dealing continuous damage.

Curtain Splash.name: Curtain Splash
Curtain Splash.description: Continously creates walls made from water columns at the enemy's location.

Dark Arrow.name: Dark Arrow
Dark Arrow.description: Fires off dark energy that homes in on an enemy.

Dark Ball.name: Dark Ball
Dark Ball.description: Unleases a sphere of darkness that slowly tracks down the enemy.

Dark Cannon.name: Dark Cannon
Dark Cannon.description: Fires off dark energy that homes in on an enemy.

Dark Laser.name: Dark Laser
Dark Laser.description: Charges dark energy before blasting enemies with a powerful beam.

Diamond Rain.name: Diamond Rain
Diamond Rain.description: Creates numerous lumps of ice that are consecutively dropped on a foe's head.

Draconic Breath.name: Draconic Breath
Draconic Breath.description: Exhales breath imbued with draconic energy, dealing continuous damage to those in front of it.

Dragon Burst.name: Dragon Burst
Dragon Burst.description: Quickly discharges draconic energy, damaging those around it.

Dragon Cannon.name: Dragon Cannon
Dragon Cannon.description: Hurls an energy ball imbued with draconic energy at an enemy.

Dragon Meteor.name: Dragon Meteor
Dragon Meteor.description: Calls down numerous small meteorites and launches them at an enemy.

Electric Ball.name: Electric Ball
Electric Ball.description: Fires an electric ball that slowly pursues an enemy.

Fire Ball.name: Fire Ball
Fire Ball.description: Creates a giant ball of flames and hurls it at an enemy.  The ball explodes over a wide area upon impact.

Flame Funnel.name: Flame Funnel
Flame Funnel.description: Creates multiple spheres of fiery energy, from which countless fireballs shoot towards the enemy.

Flame Wall.name: Flame Wall
Flame Wall.description: Creates a wall of flames at the enemy's location. The wall of flame will remain for a while, and deal damage to the enemies it touches.

Flare Arrow.name: Flare Arrow
Flare Arrow.description: Fires three flaming arrows in succession that home in on an enemy.

Flare Storm.name: Flare Storm
Flare Storm.description: Generates two flaming tornadoes on either side before launching them at an enemy.

Grass Tornado.name: Grass Tornado
Grass Tornado.description: Generates two tornadoes on either side before launching them at an enemy.

Holy Burst.name: Holy Burst
Holy Burst.description: Creates a wide explosion of light at the enemy's location and around it.

Hydro Jet.name: Hydro Jet
Hydro Jet.description: Hurls a high speed ball of water at an enemy.

Hydro Laser.name: Hydro Laser
Hydro Laser.description: Shoots pressurized water at extreme velocities, sweeping over a wide area in front of it.

Ice Missile.name: Ice Missile
Ice Missile.description: Creates ice lances in the air that fly towards enemies.

Iceberg.name: Iceberg
Iceberg.description: Summons a sharp ice lance under an enemy.

Icicle Cutter.name: Icicle Cutter
Icicle Cutter.description: Creates a crescent blade of ice and hurls it forward.

Icicle Line.name: Icicle Line
Icicle Line.description: Generates a pillar of ice that moves in a straight line.

Ignis Blast.name: Ignis Blast
Ignis Blast.description: Hurls a ball of fire straight at an enemy.

Ignis Breath.name: Ignis Breath
Ignis Breath.description: Shoots flames at an enemy, dealing continuous damage.

Ignis Rage.name: Ignis Rage
Ignis Rage.description: Energizes the surrounding ground, causing it to explode after a set amount of time.

Implode.name: Implode
Implode.description: Risks its life to cause a violent explosion. Becomes incapacitated afterwards.

Lightning Bolt.name: Lightning Bolt
Lightning Bolt.description: Charges electric energy before blasting enemies with a powerful shock.

Lightning Streak.name: Lightning Streak
Lightning Streak.description: Generates a lightning bolt that moves forward in a line.

Lightning Strike.name: Lightning Strike
Lightning Strike.description: Acts as a lightning rod, calling down thunderbolts that electrocute the surrounding area.

Lock-on Laser.name: Lock-on Laser
Lock-on Laser.description: Takes aim at an enemy before firing a super high speed laser.

Megaton Implode.name: Megaton Implode
Megaton Implode.description: Risks life to cause a massive explosion. Those who perish for their duty become glistening stars in the night sky.

Multicutter.name: Multicutter
Multicutter.description: The user fires three high-speed blades of wind in quick succession that fly straight at enemies.

Nightmare Ball.name: Nightmare Ball
Nightmare Ball.description: Creates a giant ball of darkness and hurls it at an enemy.

Pal Blast.name: Pal Blast
Pal Blast.description: Charges destructive energy before firing a high-powered beam forward across a wide area.

Plasma Funnel.name: Plasma Funnel
Plasma Funnel.description: Creates two balls of electric energy that fire numerous bolts of lightning at enemies.

Poison Blast.name: Poison Blast
Poison Blast.description: Hurls poison sludge at an enemy.

Poison Fog.name: Poison Fog
Poison Fog.description: Generates a fog of poison in front, causing the opponent to become poisoned.

Power Bomb.name: Power Bomb
Power Bomb.description: Charges a massive amount of energy before firing a large destructive ball.

Power Shot.name: Power Shot
Power Shot.description: Charges energy into a focused blast.

Rockburst.name: Rockburst
Rockburst.description: Causes the ground to shake before hurling a massive stone mass at its surroundings.

Rock Lance.name: Rock Lance
Rock Lance.description: Generates a sharp rock spear under an enemy.

Sand Tornado.name: Sand Tornado
Sand Tornado.description: Generates two sand tornadoes on either side before launching them at an enemy.

Sand Twister.name: Sand Twister
Sand Twister.description: Creates multiple sand tornadoes. The tornadoes continuously spin in circles.

Seed Machine Gun.name: Seed Machine Gun
Seed Machine Gun.description: Fires a volley of hard seeds at enemies in front of it.
Seed Machine Gun.skillFruit: Grass Skill Fruit: Seed Machine Gun

Seed Mine.name: Seed Mine
Seed Mine.description: Launches a deadly seed. If it hits an enemy, the seed explodes.

Shadow Burst.name: Shadow Burst
Shadow Burst.description: Quickly discharges dark energy, damaging those around it.

Shockwave.name: Shockwave
Shockwave.description: Quickly discharges electricity, shacking those around it.

Solar Blast.name: Solar Blast
Solar Blast.description: Charges solar energy before blasting enemies with a powerful beam.

Spark Blast.name: Spark Blast
Spark Blast.description: The user releases a lightning ball that expands outward in a forward, circular pattern.

Spine Vine.name: Spine Vine
Spine Vine.description: Generates spiny thorns that chase an enemy along the ground, piercing them from below.

Spirit Fire.name: Spirit Fire
Spirit Fire.description: Shoots fireballs towards an enemy. The fireballs explode after a short distance, generating smaller fireballs that spread forward.

Spirit Flame.name: Spirit Flame
Spirit Flame.description: Fires three balls of malice that relentlessly pursue an enemy.

Splash.name: Splash
Splash.description: Generates a column of water that travels in a straight line.

Stone Blast.name: Stone Blast
Stone Blast.description: Fires a barrage of stones forward.

Stone Cannon.name: Stone Cannon
Stone Cannon.description: Digs up a boulder and hurls it at an enemy.

Thunder Rain.name: Thunder Rain
Thunder Rain.description: Calls lightning that strikes an enemy after a set amount of time has passed.

Thunderstorm.name: Thunderstorm
Thunderstorm.description: Generates a huge tornado of lightning that moves slowly towards the enemy.

Tri-Lightning.name: Tri-Lightning
Tri-Lightning.description: Generates lightning that strikes an enemy three times from above.

TriSpark.name: TriSpark
TriSpark.description: A high-speed lightning ball that flies in a straight line. Simultaneously fires slow lightning balls that track the enemy.

Umbral Surge.name: Umbral Surge
Umbral Surge.description: Fires a high speed ball of dark energy that spreads forward in a radial shape.

Volcanic Rain.name: Volcanic Rain
Volcanic Rain.description: Fires countless volcanic bombs into the sky. After a while, the bombs rain down around their originator.

Wind Cutter.name: Wind Cutter
Wind Cutter.description: Fires a high speed blade of wind that flies straight at an enemy.
